sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Server
    participant Service

    Client->>Server: 1. Establish WebSocket connection
    Client->>Server: 2. Emit message payload
    Server->>Service: 3. Save message in DB
    Service-->>Server: 4. Saved message
    Server-->>Client: 5. Emit message to sender and receiver
    Client->>Client: 6. Update state and re-render UI